description: PIMS 1055 BD MSP PAK Mainstreaming Biodiversity Conservation in production systems in the Juniper Forest Ecosystem

subproject.description:
1. Economically, ecologically and socially sustainable utilization of Juniper Forest Ecosystem is operationalised at 4 – 6 selected valleys.
2. Mechanisms for replicating the sustainable utilization regimes across the entire Juniper Forest Ecosystems of Balochistan, and further disseminating project successes.
subproject.gender code: Gender equality as a significant objective
subproject.title: ECC-Juniper Forest Ecosystem
